OL,3,CMan who had life saved by
OL,4,Cdefibrillator urges people to maintain
OL,5,Cthem
OL,7,FRick explains: "I noticed my vision
OL,8,Fgoing a little bit fuzzy and the next
OL,9,Fthing I'm aware of is lying on the
OL,10,Ffloor, shirt undone wondering what on
OL,11,Fearth had happened."
OL,13,FRick's life was saved by a nearby
OL,14,Fdefibrillator after a resident knew
OL,15,Fhow to use it but he fears not enough
OL,16,Fpeople are trained.
OL,18,FGuernsey has more than 150 devices
OL,19,Faround the island, which are
OL,20,Fmaintained by volunteers.
