OL,3,CMan who had life saved by
OL,4,Cdefibrillator urges people to maintain
OL,5,Cthem
OL,7,FDefibrillator Guardian Ellie Smith
OL,8,Fsays: "We have an app that we use so
OL,9,Fit tells us what to check so we make
OL,10,Fsure that it's clean, serviceable and
OL,11,Fhasn't been tampered with or damaged.
OL,13,F"We make sure that everything inside
OL,14,Fis working so that if it needs to be
OL,15,Fused at any time, it's ready to go."
OL,17,FPersonal Trainer Claire Luvin saved
OL,18,Fsomeone's life after they went into
OL,19,Fcardiac arrest on a squash court.
