OL,3,CMan who had life saved by
OL,4,Cdefibrillator urges people to maintain
OL,5,Cthem
OL,7,FShe says: "I literally just had CPR
OL,8,Ftraining about 10 days before, so I
OL,9,Fknew what I was doing. I stayed calm
OL,10,Fand then paramedics took over."
OL,12,FGerry Le Roy from the Cardiac Action
OL,13,FGroup adds: "It's not just about
OL,14,Fsaving lives, but the quality of those
OL,15,Flives and that person's family as well.
